fr.reflexe.viewshell.api.connector

Interface IPlatformConnector

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAttachable, IConnector, IHttpEndPoint, Iterable<ISource>

    @SystemService
public interface IPlatformConnector
extends IConnector, IHttpEndPoint
    Connector to an OpenAGE platform server. Sources for this connector type correspond to OpenAGE "transactions", and are backed by OpenAGE "tables". One table may have multiple associated transactions.

    Thread safety: implementations are required to be safe for concurrent read/write access.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    REFLEXE Technologies
    See Also:
    IPlatformService.addConnector(String)
